Baiwei jí o hodině.

161
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,670
Já ... ne ... nejím.

162
00:09:50,110 --> 00:09:50,910
Vidíte?

163
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:52,760
Co je to?

164
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,580
Nechtěla jsem nic říkat,

165
00:09:56,590 --> 00:09:57,670
ale tys jedla

166
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:59,030
jednu po druhé

167
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,470
dost hlučným způsobem

168
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:02,400
a mě to vyrušovalo.

169
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,870
<i>Tak hnusné sušenky

170
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,840
<i>by ani žebrák neochutnal.

171
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,280
To jsi tak dlouho nejedla,

172
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:09,200
