188
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,230
No a co?

189
00:11:14,230 --> 00:11:15,190
Co tu děláš?

190
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:18,880
Postarat se o tebe.

191
00:11:19,590 --> 00:11:21,150
Povinností mužů je starat se

192
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:21,880
