Pospěš si.

205
00:11:42,590 --> 00:11:43,900
Za něco tak malého se nevejdu?

206
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:44,980
Gauč. Za gauč.

207
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,030
Pospěš si. Schovej se!

208
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:50,560
<i>Co se děje?

209
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:52,080
<i>Protahuji si svaly.

210
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:53,580
<i>Protahuješ si svaly? Nic ti není?

211
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:54,150
Nic.

212
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:55,890
