234
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:36,030
A co ústřicovou polévku?

235
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,800
<i>Ne. V žádném případě!

236
00:12:38,470 --> 00:12:39,270
Tak jo, dobře.

237
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:39,960
Rozumím.

238
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:41,150
Lehni si a spi.

239
00:12:41,230 --> 00:12:42,030
Jo.

240
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:45,680
A ještě, Xiaoxi.

241
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,440
<i>Co zase?

242
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:48,590
Co když

243
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:49,790
zajdu nakoupit?

244
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:50,470
